    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given that the ASTM F1717 protocol prescribes a single standardized test configuration and the output comparison results demonstrate agreement across all three QoIs well within the pre-established acceptance bounds. The overall evidence package supports medium assurance for the intended regulatory decision.",
